== 投票權 ==
居於直布羅陀的英國公民、[[爱尔兰|愛爾蘭]]公民及[[英联邦|英聯邦]]公民都可在今次公投中投票。除了愛爾蘭、[[马耳他|馬耳他]]和[[賽普勒斯|塞浦路斯]]，居於直布羅陀的其他歐盟成員國公民都不可以投票<ref>{{cite web|title=Background to the UK's EU referendum 2016|url=http://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/research/eu-referendum/background-uk-eu-referendum-2016/|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624120337/http://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/research/eu-referendum/background-uk-eu-referendum-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。投票年齡門檻與英國本地一樣，均為18歲<ref name="Dathan">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/eu-referendum-outcome-on-a-knife-edge-new-poll-reveals-a6773551.html|title=EU referendum outcome on a knife edge, new poll reveals|first=Matt|last=Dathan|newspaper=The Independent|date=2015-12-15|accessdate=2015-12-16|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215151938/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/eu-referendum-outcome-on-a-knife-edge-new-poll-reveals-a6773551.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。公投投票時間為[[欧洲中部夏令时间|欧洲中部夏令时间]]2016年6月23日早上7點至晚上10點，當英國的所有票站在晚上11點關閉後，點票隨即開始。

== 已登記選民 ==
2016年6月9日為登記做選民的限期。同月21日，選舉委員會公佈英國和直布羅陀已登記選民的臨時數字，數字包括所有英聯邦和愛爾蘭選民<ref>{{cite web|title=Provisional electorate figures published ahead of the EU referendum|url=http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/i-am-a/journalist/electoral-commission-media-centre/news-releases-referendums/provisional-electorate-figures-published-ahead-of-the-eu-referendum|accessdate=2016-06-21|archive-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623084724/http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/i-am-a/journalist/electoral-commission-media-centre/news-releases-referendums/provisional-electorate-figures-published-ahead-of-the-eu-referendum|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終官方數字在6月23日晚上9點公佈<ref>{{cite web|title=EU Referendum results|url=http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/find-information-by-subject/elections-and-referendums/upcoming-elections-and-referendums/eu-referendum/electorate-and-count-information|accessdate=2016-07-13|archive-date=2017-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129082658/http://www.electoralcommission.org.uk/find-information-by-subject/elections-and-referendums/upcoming-elections-and-referendums/eu-referendum/electorate-and-count-information|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
